<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>{{ subject }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f2f2f2;font-family:'Malgun Gothic',Arial,sans-serif;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f2f2f2;padding:24px 0;">
<tr><td align="center">
<table role="presentation" width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;">
<tr>
<td style="background-color:#1a237e;padding:20px 24px;">
<span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;">주요뉴스 다이제스트</span><br>
<span style="color:#c5cae9;font-size:13px;">{{ generated_at }}</span>
</td>
</tr>
{% for keyword, items in items_by_keyword.items() %}
<tr>
<td style="padding:16px 24px 4px 24px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#e8eaf6;color:#1a237e;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;">{{ keyword }}</span>
</td>
</tr>
{% for item in items %}
<tr>
<td style="padding:8px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid #eeeeee;">
<a href="{{ item.link }}" style="color:#1a237e;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;">{{ item.title }}</a>
<div style="color:#666666;font-size:13px;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.4;">{{ item.llm_summary or item.summary }}</div>
<div style="color:#999999;font-size:11px;margin-top:4px;">{{ item.source }}{% if item.published %} · {{ item.published }}{% endif %}</div>
</td>
</tr>
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
<tr>
<td style="padding:16px 24px;color:#aaaaaa;font-size:11px;">
주요뉴스 자동화 메일전송 프로그램이 자동으로 생성한 다이제스트입니다.
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
